nk" rel="noopener">Decisions about Decisions: Practical Reason in Ordinary Life</a> .”</p><div></div><p><span id="more-318192"></span></p><p></p><h3> Ted Seides Authored Books</h3><p> <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0857198866/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Capital Allocators: How the world&#39;s elite money managers lead and invest</a></strong> by Ted Seides<br /> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0857198866/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-318111" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seides-2.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="391" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seides-2.jpg 319w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seides-2-192x300.jpg 192w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/seides-2-250x391.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p><p> <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1119134188/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">So You Want to Start a Hedge Fund: Lessons for Managers and Allocators</a></strong> by Ted Seides<br /> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1119134188/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-318112" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/soyouwant.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="353" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/soyouwant.jpg 353w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/soyouwant-212x300.jpg 212w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/soyouwant-250x353.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p><p></p><h3> Ted Seides Favorite Books</h3><p> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1416544690/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Pioneering Portfolio Management: An Unconventional Approach to Institutional Investment</